![](Images/Aljazeera Chinese/2023-06-25T13-09-00/52-1687697738.jpg)Despite being attacked near Volne, the Wagner Force did not seem to encounter too much resistance to Moscow.

By Saturday, the 24th, Wagner's founder and leader Yfgeni Porigin and his troops left Rostov less than 24 hours after the rebellion started.

